  ID: MalteseSoldier
  Name: Pietro
  Icon: {fileID: 409668665, guid: 4147f2bc6fccc974f937adc9cd1a5700, type: 3}
  Description: "Wound: A musket ball lodged in the thigh, bone shattered, blood soaking
    his torn hose.\n\nStory: Pietro, a Maltese farmer conscripted into the fight,
    weeps openly. He speaks of his wife hiding in Mdina with their newborn son, of
    the vineyard they had just planted that spring. He begs you to save his leg,
    not for himself, but so he can walk home to them \u2014 otherwise they will starve
    without his hands.\n\n\nRequired bandages to heal: 2"
